[SP-v4] B2 verdict: pass

No FA clears the bar. Janson Junk (the lone borderline) has IP/GS P45 and BB/9 P95 edges over Cantillo, but Whiff% P0 and K9 6.45 gut K upside, and he's on IL15. The remaining FAs are relievers (Latz 1 GS/22 G, Fuentes 1 GS/15 G, Drohan 2 GS/12 G), mirror Cantillo's weaknesses without offsetting strengths (Rocker, Bassitt, Severino all BB/9 P0-P25), or have no credible sample (Sandlin BBE 0 Savant, 2 GS). Cantillo's BB/9 P0 is a real weakness but his Whiff% P60, xwOBACON P80, and 21d delta −.018 (improving) keep him above every available FA on net profile.

